      <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold lh-1 text-body-emphasis mb-4">About Blogify</h1>
      <p class="fs-5">
        Blogify is a dynamic web application designed to provide a simple and elegant platform for sharing your thoughts and ideas. It was built as a project to demonstrate proficiency in modern web development technologies.
      </p>
      <p class="fs-5">
        This project focuses on the fundamentals of back-end development, including routing, middleware, and server-side rendering, without the complexity of a database. All posts are session-based, meaning they will disappear when the server is restarted. This allows for a focus on the core CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) functionality.
      </p>
      <hr class="my-4">
      <h2 class="fw-bold lh-1 text-body-emphasis mb-3">Core Technologies</h2>
      <ul class="fs-5">
